prompts.frontCover: 2D flat illustration for a greeting card, full shot. A charming and humorous cartoon scene on a cute, stylized beach. Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are the central characters, drawn in a playful illustrated style. Lao Lao, wearing her light blue sweatshirt, is playfully trying to balance a giant, oversized boba tea drink on her head, laughing with a big, joyful expression. Jordan, in his tan hoodie, stands next to her with a look of mock concentration, holding his hands out as if ready to catch the wobbling drink. The boba tea itself is comically large, with huge tapioca pearls visible through the plastic cup. The beach is whimsical, with soft-toned sand and gentle, cartoonish waves lapping the shore. The botanical element is integrated through lush, oversized monstera leaves and hibiscus flowers framing the scene like a natural archway. The art style is clean with simple line work and a soft, pastel color palette, primarily featuring blues, greens, and sandy tones. Centered in the open space below the archway and above the characters, the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, flowing, hand-drawn cursive script. The overall composition is balanced, lighthearted, and full of personality.
